description: I needed someone special for a Friday the 13th shoot. Someone who I could push a little harder. Take things a little farther. Someone hot, sexy, tough and not afraid to shoot on an unlucky day. I…uh..WE, got Isis Love. How’d we do? I want to thank Isis for her terrific work in this shoot. She suffered beautifully for us, overcame more of her water phobia problems and in general showed us once again why she is one of the best in the biz.
title: Isis Love
